\c 12
\s UJesu uchasisa umlayo wesabatha
\p
\v 1 Ngalesosikhathi uJesu wadabula emasimini amabele ngesabatha; njalo abafundi bakhe babelambile\x + Mark. 2.23-28. Luka 6.1-5.\x*, baqala ukukha izikhwebu, badla\x + Dute. 23.25.\x*.
\v 2 Kodwa abaFarisi be\add ku\add*bona bathi kuye: Khangela, abafundi bakho benza okungavunyelwanga ukwenziwa ngesabatha\x + Eks. 20.9.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa wathi kubo: Kalifundanga yini uDavida akwenzayo\x + 1 Sam. 21.6.\x*, mhla elambile yena lababelaye;
\v 4 ukuthi wangena njani endlini kaNkulunkulu, wadla izinkwa zokubukiswa, ayengavunyelwa ukuzidla, ngitsho lababelaye\x + Eks. 25.30. Levi 24.5-8.\x*, ngaphandle kwabapristi bodwa\x + Levi 24.9. Eks. 29.32,33. Levi 8.31.\x*?
\v 5 Ingabe kalifundanga yini emlayweni, ukuthi ngamasabatha abapristi bayalona isabatha ethempelini, bangabi lacala\x + Nani 28.9,10. Joha. 7.22.\x*?
\v 6 Kodwa ngithi kini: Kukhona lapha omkhulu kulethempeli\x + Hag. 2.7,9. Mal. 3.1. Mat. 12.41,42.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa aluba belisazi ukuthi kutshoni \add ukuthi\x + 9.13.\x*\add*: Ngifisa isihawu hatshi umhlatshelo, ngabe kalibalahlanga abangelacala.
\v 8 Ngoba iNdodana yomuntu iyiNkosi leyesabatha\x + Hos. 6.6.\x*.
\s UJesu usilisa ngesabatha
\p
\v 9 Futhi wasuka lapho wangena esinagogeni labo;
\v 10 njalo khangela, kwakukhona umuntu olesandla esitshwabheneyo\x + Mark. 3.1-6. Luka 6.6-11.\x*; basebembuza besithi: Kuvunyelwe yini ukusilisa ngamasabatha? ukuze bambeke icala.
\v 11 Kodwa wathi kubo: Nguwuphi umuntu phakathi kwenu, elemvu eyodwa, futhi uba yona iwele emgodini ngesabatha, ongayikuyibamba a\add yi\add*khuphule\x + Luka 13.14; 14.3. Joha. 9.16.\x*?
\v 12 Umuntu uyedlula-ke kangakanani imvu\x + 10.31.\x*! Ngakho kuvunyelwe ukwenza okuhle ngamasabatha.
\v 13 Wasesithi kumuntu: Yelula isandla sakho. Wase\add s\add*elula, sasesisiliswa saphila njengesinye.
\s Inceku ekhethiweyo
\p
\v 14 Basebephuma abaFarisi becebisana ngaye, ukuthi bangambulala njani\x + Joha. 5.18; 10.39; 11.53.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa uJesu esekwazi wasuka lapho\x + Mark. 3.7. Mat. 10.23.\x*; amaxuku amakhulu asemlandela, wasebasilisa bonke\x + 19.2.\x*.
\v 16 Wasebalayisisa ukuthi bangamvezi\x + Mark. 1.25; 3.12; 8.30. Luka 4.41; 9.21. Mat. 8.4.\x*;
\v 17 ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa nguIsaya umprofethi, ukuthi:
\v 18 Khangela, inceku yami engiyikhethileyo; othandekayo wami\x + Isa. 42.1-3.\x* othokoza ngaye umphefumulo wami; ngizabeka uMoya wami phezu kwakhe, njalo uzatshumayela ukwahlulela kwabezizwe.
\v 19 Kayikubangisa, kayikumemeza, njalo kakho ozalizwa ilizwi lakhe ezindleleni.
\v 20 Umhlanga ofecekileyo kayikuwephula, lentambo yesibane ethunqayo kayikuyicitsha, aze aphumelelise ukwahlulela\x + 3.17.\x* ekunqobeni\x + 1 Kor. 15.54.\x*.
\v 21 Lezizwe zizathemba ebizweni lakhe\x + Isa. 42.4.\x*.
\s Isono sokuhlambaza
\p
\v 22 Kwasekulethwa kuye ongenwe lidimoni, \add ey\add*isiphofu lesimungulu; wasemsilisa, kwaze kwathi isiphofu \add esiy\add*isimungulu sakhuluma njalo sabona\x + 4.24.\x*.
\v 23 Asemangala amaxuku wonke athi\x + Luka 2.47.\x*: Lo kayisiyo yini iNdodana kaDavida\x + 9.27.\x*?
\v 24 Kodwa abaFarisi sebezwile bathi: Lumuntu kakhuphi amadimoni, ngaphandle ngoBhelezebhule inkosi yamadimoni\x + Mark. 3.22.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa uJesu, eseyazi imicabango yabo, wathi kubo\x + 9.4.\x*: Wonke umbuso owehlukene umelene lawo ngokwawo uyachitheka; lawo wonke umuzi kumbe indlu eyehlukene imelene layo ngokwayo ingeze yema.
\v 26 Njalo uba uSathane ekhupha uSathane, wehlukene emelene laye ngokwakhe; pho umbuso wakhe uzakuma njani\x + Mark. 3.23-27. Luka 11.17-22.\x*?
\v 27 Futhi uba mina ngikhupha amadimoni ngoBhelezebhule, amadodana enu akhupha ngobani? Ngakho wona azakuba ngabagwebi benu\x + Luka 11.19. 2 Kho. 2.3.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa uba mina ngikhupha amadimoni ngoMoya kaNkulunkulu, umbuso kaNkulunkulu usufikile kini\x + Roma 9.31. 2 Kor. 10.14. Fil. 3.16. 1 Thes. 2.16.\x*.
\v 29 Kumbe umuntu angangena njani endlini yesiqhwaga aphange impahla yaso, ngaphandle kokuthi asibophe kuqala isiqhwaga\x + Isa. 49.24.\x*? Abesephanga-ke indlu yaso\x + Isa. 53.12. Kol. 2.15.\x*.
\v 30 Ongelami, umelene lami, longabuthi lami, uyachithiza\x + Luka 11.23. Mark. 9.40. Luka 9.50.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Ngakho ngithi kini: Abantu bazathethelelwa sonke isono lokuhlambaza\x + 12.31,32, Mark. 3.28-30. Luka 12.10. 1 Joha. 5.16.\x*; kodwa ukuhlambaza uMoya kakuyikuthethelelwa abantu\x + 12.32.\x*.
\v 32 Lalowo okhuluma ilizwi elimelana leNdodana yomuntu\x + 11.19; 13.55-57. Joha. 7.12,20.\x*, uzathethelelwa\x + 1 Tim. 1.13.\x*; kodwa lowo okhuluma emelana loMoya oyiNgcwele, kayikuthethelelwa, kungeyisikho kulesisikhathi loba kwesizayo.
\p
\v 33 Loba yenzani isihlahla sibe ngesilungileyo, lesithelo saso sibe ngesilungileyo, kumbe lenze isihlahla sibe sibi, lesithelo saso sibe sibi\x + 7.16-20.\x*, ngoba isihlahla saziwa ngesithelo\x + Luka 6.44.\x*.
\v 34 Nzalo yezinyoka, lingakhuluma njani izinto ezinhle, libabi\x + 3.7; 23.33.\x*? Ngoba umlomo ukhuluma ngokugcwala kwenhliziyo.
\v 35 Umuntu olungileyo ukhupha izinto ezilungileyo kokuligugu elilungileyo lenhliziyo; lomuntu omubi ukhupha izinto ezimbi kokuligugu elibi\x + Luka 6.45.\x*.
\v 36 Kodwa ngithi kini: Lonke ilizwi eliyize abalikhulumayo abantu, bazaziphendulela ngalo ngosuku lokwahlulela.
\v 37 Ngoba ngamazwi akho uzalungisiswa, langamazwi akho uzalahlwa\x + Jak. 3.2-12.\x*.
\s Abafuna isibonakaliso
\p
\v 38 Abanye bababhali labaFarisi basebephendula, bathi: Mfundisi, sifuna ukubona isibonakaliso esivela kuwe\x + 6.1. Mark. 8.11,12. Luka 11.16,29. Joha. 2.18; 6.30. 1 Kor. 1.22. Joha. 4.48.\x*.
\v 39 Kodwa waphendula wathi kubo: Isizukulwana esibi\x + Luka 11.29-32.\x* lesifebayo sidinga isibonakaliso; kodwa kasiyikunikwa isibonakaliso, ngaphandle kwesibonakaliso sikaJona umprofethi\x + Isa. 57.3. Mat. 16.4. Mark. 8.38. Jak. 4.4.\x*.
\v 40 Ngoba njengalokhu uJona waba sesiswini sensikabayitshiye insuku ezintathu lobusuku obuthathu, ngokunjalo iNdodana yomuntu izakuba semathunjini omhlaba insuku ezintathu lobusuku obuthathu\x + Jona 1.17.\x*.
\v 41 Amadoda eNineve\x + Jona 1.2.\x* azasukuma ekugwetshweni kanye lalesisizukulwana\x + 12.32.\x*, asilahle\x + 12.42. Heb. 11.7. Jer. 3.11. Hez. 16.51,52. Roma 2.27.\x*; ngoba aphenduka ngokutshumayela kukaJona\x + Jona 3.5-9.\x*; njalo khangelani, omkhulu kuloJona ulapha\x + 12.6.\x*.
\v 42 Indlovukazi yeningizimu izasukuma ekugwetshweni kanye lalesisizukulwana\x + 1 Kho. 10.1.\x*, isilahle; ngoba yavela emikhawulweni yomhlaba u\add kuza\add*kuzwa inhlakanipho kaSolomoni\x + 12.42. Heb. 11.7. Jer. 3.11. Hez. 16.51,52. Roma 2.27.\x*; njalo khangelani, omkhulu kuloSolomoni ulapha\x + 12.6.\x*.
\s Ukuphenduka okungaphelelanga
\p
\v 43 Kodwa nxa umoya ongcolileyo esephumile emuntwini\x + Luka 11.24-26.\x*, uyahamba adabule indawo ezomileyo, edinga ukuphumula, kodwa enga\add ku\add*tholi.
\v 44 Abesesithi: Ngizabuyela endlini yami engaphuma kuyo; njalo esefikile ayifice ize, ithanyelwe\x + 2 Pet. 2.17. Juda 12. Hlab. 63.1.Jer. 2.6.\x*, njalo ilungisiwe.
\v 45 Abesehamba athathe kanye laye abanye omoya abayisikhombisa ababi kulaye uqobo, besebengena bahlale khona\x + 23.29.\x*; njalo ukucina kwalowomuntu kube kubi kulokuqala. Kuzakuba njalo lakulesisizukulwana esibi\x + 2 Pet. 2.20. Joha. 5.14. Heb. 6.4-6; 10.26,29. 2 Pet. 2.21,22.\x*.
\s Izihlobo zikaJesu eziyizo
\p
\v 46 Kwathi esakhuluma emaxukwini, khangela, unina\x + Mark. 3.31-35. Luka 8.19-21.\x* labafowabo bema ngaphandle, bedinga ukukhuluma laye.
\v 47 Omunye wasesithi kuye: Khangela, unyoko labafowenu bemi phandle, bedinga ukukhuluma lawe.
\v 48 Kodwa waphendula wathi komtshelileyo: Ngubani umama? Labafowethu ngobani?
\v 49 Waseselulela isandla sakhe kubafundi bakhe wathi: Khangelani, umama labafowethu\x + 13.55. Mark. 6.3. Joha. 2.12; 7.3,5,10. Seb. 1.14. 1 Kor. 9.5. Gal. 1.19. Mark. 3.21.\x*.
\v 50 Ngoba loba ngubani owenza intando\x + Joha. 15.14. Heb. 2.11.\x* kaBaba osemazulwini, nguye ongumfowethu lodadewethu lomama\x + 7.11.\x*.